♪Crossing the sea within the sea♪

6
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:43,960
♪Courage fills the heart♪

7
00:00:44,490 --> 00:00:49,270
♪The more you venture,
the freer your soul is♪

8
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:52,970
♪Even when destiny looms high♪

9
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:57,180
♪There will always be brilliance♪

10
00:00:58,210 --> 00:01:01,190
♪Shining through♪

11
00:01:01,310 --> 00:01:04,480
♪Braving the storm♪

12
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:07,510
♪Fearless of failure♪

13
00:01:07,510 --> 00:01:13,360
♪Toward the faraway land
where the heart longs♪

14
