♪Together we embark on a new chapter♪

17
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,907
=The Land of Warriors=

18
00:01:27,908 --> 00:01:29,980
(Adapted from Tangjia Sanshao's novel
"Soul Land")

19
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:34,300
=Episode 27=

20
00:01:48,970 --> 00:01:49,780
How do you feel now?

21
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:52,660
Was the young man who beat me Tang San?

22
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:53,744
It's a misunderstanding.

23
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,450
This is a misunderstanding.

24
00:01:55,970 --> 00:01:57,090
You probably lost your temper

25
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:58,020
and started it.

26
00:01:58,020 --> 00:01:58,730
And

27
00:01:58,730 --> 00:02:00,020
the chief didn't recognize you,

28
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:01,220
so he acted in self-defense.

29
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,060
Did I get it right,

30
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:02,780
Old Goat?

31
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:04,500
It must be.

32
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:06,700
He likes to joke around.

33
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:07,780
He's humorous.

34
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,380
Exactly.

35
00:02:08,380 --> 00:02:09,820
Actually, Tang San is a nice person.

36
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:10,672
Before you arrive,

37
00:02:10,670 --> 00:02:13,390
Elephant Armored Tribe, the lackey
of Martial Soul Hall, attacked us.

38
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,100
Chief stepped up
and fought them off.

39
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:15,490
Yes.

40
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:17,210
The reason why
he established the Tang Clan

41
00:02:17,216 --> 00:02:18,300
was to unite all of us

42
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:20,420
and stand against Martial Soul Hall.

43
00:02:20,930 --> 00:02:22,860
He's Master Tang Hao's son.

44
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,730
But don't worry.

45
00:02:23,730 --> 00:02:26,770
He absolutely won't merge
with the Haotian Sect.

46
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:32,820
The three of you

47
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:34,980
won't stop calling him a chief

48
00:02:35,450 --> 00:02:36,930
and even said he was Tang Hao's son.

49
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:40,650
Are you hiding some big plan from me?

50
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,420
Old Goat,

51
00:02:44,980 --> 00:02:45,730
as of now,

52
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:47,792
Martial Soul Hall is
overwhelmingly powerful.

53
00:02:47,824 --> 00:02:49,140
If our tribes stand alone,

54
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:51,580
we won't survive down the road.

55
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:53,890
Tang Clan

56
00:02:54,330 --> 00:02:55,930
means a different story to us.

57
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:58,580
But both of you got off
on the wrong foot.

58
00:02:58,580 --> 00:03:00,210
Says who?

59
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,770
Am I that unreasonable to you?

60
00:03:03,210 --> 00:03:04,330
His father and he

61
00:03:04,330 --> 00:03:05,210
are not the same.

62
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:07,380
I know the difference.

63
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:19,420
Besides,

64
00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:23,580
Tang San helped me mature my herb,

65
00:03:24,770 --> 00:03:26,820
and we got to know each other
through a fight.

66
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:29,820
I have a good impression of him.

67
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,300
This young man

68
00:03:31,650 --> 00:03:33,210
is ambitious and insightful.

69
00:03:36,330 --> 00:03:37,330
He's capable as well.

70
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:40,930
So you won't argue over this, will you?

71
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:42,610
What's there to argue about?

72
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:44,770
I just want to know how he's doing now.

73
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,512
He got pierced
by the Soul Breaking Spear.

74
00:03:46,510 --> 00:03:48,810
If he doesn't get treatment,
there could be side effects.

75
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:49,420
Let's go

76
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,330
and check on him.

77
00:03:50,330 --> 00:03:53,100
That young man is more capable
than we thought.

78
00:03:53,330 --> 00:03:55,450
His injury has already
healed on its own.

79
00:03:55,450 --> 00:03:56,420
- Exactly.
- Yes.

80
00:03:56,610 --> 00:03:57,420
It healed on its own?

81
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,050
Exactly.

82
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,930
A young man with only over level 60

83
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,260
can be that amazing?

84
00:04:02,730 --> 00:04:03,700
And all his friends

85
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:05,890
are also more capable
than we were back then.

86
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:07,450
Old Goat,

87
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,650
let me tell you a secret.

88
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:13,980
Tang San has prepared
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng for you.

89
00:04:14,170 --> 00:04:14,770
What?

90
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,260
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng?

91
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:18,380
Right.

92
00:04:18,970 --> 00:04:21,140
We wouldn't have to fight
if he had shown that earlier.

93
00:04:21,952 --> 00:04:23,180
He didn't feel the pain,

94
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:24,820
but I sure did.

95
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,380
Looks like

96
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:30,290
our four single attribute tribes

97
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:32,260
are going to reunite.

98
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:43,940
Wu,

99
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,210
how do you feel now?

100
00:05:20,090 --> 00:05:20,770
Wu.

101
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:42,770
Wu.

102
00:06:09,650 --> 00:06:10,260
San,

103
00:06:10,416 --> 00:06:11,380
I can't fall asleep.

104
00:06:26,096 --> 00:06:27,090
What are you doing?

105
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:28,850
Why are you nervous?

106
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,580
We used to sleep in the same room

107
00:06:30,580 --> 00:06:31,850
back at Nuoding Academy.

108
00:06:32,410 --> 00:06:34,060
People with an honest mind

109
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,580
won't overthink so much.

110
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:47,540
♪The wind sways,
trembling the moonlight♪

111
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:51,700
♪Spreading over the Xingdou forest♪

112
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:55,020
♪Your image imprinted on my heart♪

113
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:57,940
♪No matter where I go♪

114
00:06:58,420 --> 00:07:00,860
♪If fate stirs up waves♪

115
00:07:03,808 --> 00:07:05,060
This isn't a hallucination.

116
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,660
♪Without retreating♪

117
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,060
Wu.

118
00:07:15,783 --> 00:07:18,743
♪For you, I renounce my dreams♪

119
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:22,700
♪With unwavering love
and profound devotion♪

120
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:26,140
♪I'll use a lifetime of courage♪

121
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:27,940
Wu,

122
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,020
I missed you so much.

123
00:07:30,736 --> 00:07:32,576
♪Enduring immense suffering
does not matter♪

124
00:07:34,210 --> 00:07:34,650
Wu,

125
00:07:34,944 --> 00:07:36,096
let me show you something.

126
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:41,260
♪I must♪

127
00:07:41,728 --> 00:07:42,848
I've recorded all the views

128
00:07:42,912 --> 00:07:44,530
and delicious food I've seen and tried.

129
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:46,144
I hope that one day, when you wake up,

130
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,890
I could take you to each place

131
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:50,060
and let you try everything
you might like.

132
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:51,180
I record everything.

133
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:52,060
Wu,

134
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:52,530
look.

135
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:56,660
♪Combing through a lifetime
of entwined moments♪

136
00:07:58,090 --> 00:07:58,580
Sorry,

137
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:00,940
I'm hurting you.

138
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:04,330
While you were away,

139
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:07,770
I kept telling myself
that I mustn't stop.

140
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,970
Every minute I waste

141
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,500
is wasting your life.

142
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:12,890
But now,

143
00:08:14,530 --> 00:08:15,940
I won't let anyone hurt you,

144
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,650
and nothing

145
00:08:18,768 --> 00:08:20,368
can take you away from me again.

146
00:08:20,416 --> 00:08:23,140
♪For you, I renounce my dreams♪

147
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:27,210
♪With unwavering love
and profound devotion♪

148
00:08:27,210 --> 00:08:27,620
Wu,

149
00:08:28,176 --> 00:08:28,848
what's wrong?

150
00:08:28,890 --> 00:08:29,984
Why aren't you talking?

151
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:35,180
♪I will protect your peace
for a lifetime♪

152
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:37,500
♪Enduring immense suffering
does not matter♪

153
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,460
♪I'll face endless suffering
without regret♪

154
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:42,140
Wu,

155
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,290
can you hear me?

156
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:46,650
I'm Tang San.

157
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:48,340
Your San.

158
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:52,890
(San.)

159
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:54,770
(San.)

160
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:07,980
Wu?

161
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:11,740
San.

162
00:09:23,648 --> 00:09:24,464
It's really you.

163
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:28,260
Why are you in my Spiritual Sea?

164
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:29,980
What's wrong

165
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:31,500
with your body?

166
00:09:31,984 --> 00:09:32,752
Looks like

167
00:09:32,768 --> 00:09:35,104
the effect of the Millennium
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng

168
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:37,220
isn't inferior to Decade Millennium
Grade Nine Ginseng King.

169
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,380
After I accidentally ate it,

170
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,740
not only did my body restore,

171
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,530
but also part of my consciousness.

172
00:09:43,340 --> 00:09:45,216
However, my consciousness
isn't strong enough,

173
00:09:45,456 --> 00:09:47,260
so I have to stay in your Spiritual Sea.

174
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,650
Are you saying

175
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,380
that your body is unconscious

176
00:09:50,496 --> 00:09:52,496
and you can only talk to me
in my Spiritual Sea?

177
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:54,690
Wu,

178
00:09:55,264 --> 00:09:56,890
if I reach the soul power of nine rings

179
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,648
and return your soul bones
and soul rings to you,

180
00:09:59,696 --> 00:10:01,504
your consciousness will return
to your body

181
00:10:01,530 --> 00:10:02,220
and revive?

182
00:10:02,690 --> 00:10:03,050
No.

183
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:05,140
You can't risk all your soul power

184
00:10:05,216 --> 00:10:07,072
and remove the soul bones to revive me.

185
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:08,890
That's too dangerous.

186
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:09,740
I won't agree.

187
00:10:11,890 --> 00:10:13,140
This is just nothing

188
00:10:13,552 --> 00:10:15,152
compared to a double sacrifice.

189
00:10:18,570 --> 00:10:19,170
Wu,

190
00:10:20,810 --> 00:10:22,260
no matter what the price is,

191
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:24,650
reviving you

192
00:10:25,690 --> 00:10:26,930
is something I must do.

193
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:35,410
San,

194
00:10:36,410 --> 00:10:37,860
I'm very satisfied

195
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:39,860
to be with you here.

196
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:42,650
I may not

197
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:44,690
be able to control my own body yet,

198
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:49,530
but I can talk to you
anytime and anywhere.

199
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:53,740
From now on, the Spiritual Sea
is a home to me.

200
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:56,260
Don't think I'm annoying.

201
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:02,410
How could I ever think that way?

202
00:11:02,608 --> 00:11:04,530
I'm more worried you'd think
I talk too much.

203
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:10,050
During the time you were gone,

204
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:13,050
I had so much I wanted to tell you.

205
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:26,820
♪If separation is for our next meeting♪

206
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:33,580
♪My graceful longing
always reaches for the stars♪

207
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:39,020
San,

208
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:40,740
now,

209
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:43,050
I can feel every thought you have

210
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:45,170
and stay with you day and night.

211
00:11:45,696 --> 00:11:47,340
Please don't lose all your cultivation

212
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:49,140
to revive me.

213
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:50,890
Promise me, yes?

214
00:11:51,392 --> 00:11:52,650
I can promise you anything

215
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:54,410
except for this.

216
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:57,660
♪If I need you♪

217
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:01,140
♪The unspoken answer in my eyes♪

218
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:04,500
♪You will understand♪

219
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:08,580
♪If I love you♪

220
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:13,940
♪Your heartbeat resonates in my heart♪

221
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:17,100
San,

222
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:18,100
help me.

223
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:20,620
♪In my world♪

224
00:12:22,140 --> 00:12:27,180
♪I want to be your
never-changing bright day♪

225
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:33,860
♪Burning the dark nights to protect you♪

226
00:12:35,980 --> 00:12:38,860
♪They must go through me to harm you♪

227
00:12:39,770 --> 00:12:40,570
Is it done?

228
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:41,930
Yes.

229
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:47,700
♪For you, I am unafraid to perish♪

230
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:52,620
♪If I love you♪

231
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:54,020
Wu,

232
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:56,170
let me put on my clothes for you.

233
00:12:56,770 --> 00:12:57,570
Later,

234
00:12:57,616 --> 00:12:59,568
I'll have Rongrong buy
suitable clothes for you.

235
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:03,060
♪You will understand♪

236
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:06,620
♪If I love you♪

237
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:07,530
Wu,

238
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:08,860
don't eat this.

239
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:12,380
No, don't eat this.

240
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:12,890
Wu,

241
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:14,100
don't eat this.

242
00:13:17,328 --> 00:13:18,500
(Is it not obvious enough?)

243
00:13:18,930 --> 00:13:19,690
(I'm hungry.)

244
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:21,530
Oh, right.

245
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:26,540
♪Igniting the corner you existed in♪

246
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:29,500
♪Let the outcome leave us with regret♪

247
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:33,060
♪Reviving once again♪

248
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:36,620
♪If I love you♪

249
00:13:37,260 --> 00:13:40,220
♪If I need you♪

250
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:43,740
♪Bringing you to see
the surging tides of the world♪

251
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:47,140
♪With my vision♪

252
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:50,540
♪If I love you♪

253
00:13:51,458 --> 00:13:56,298
♪Embracing you in every life♪

254
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:01,260
♪Once you smile, my world♪

255
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:04,020
♪Clears up♪

256
00:14:24,050 --> 00:14:24,740
Wu,

257
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:25,930
I'm Rongrong.

258
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:27,140
She's Zhuqing.

259
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,620
Don't you recognize us?

260
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,260
Could it be that
she only acts on instinct

261
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:33,712
before her consciousness is restored?

262
00:14:39,810 --> 00:14:40,570
Wu,

263
00:14:41,770 --> 00:14:42,570
call me big sister.

264
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:44,380
(Zhuqing,)

265
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:45,690
(don't take advantage of me.)

266
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:46,944
(I'm the big sister here.)

267
00:14:49,690 --> 00:14:50,740
Let me remind you this.

268
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:53,570
Wu's consciousness is now
in my Spiritual Sea.

269
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:56,050
We're symbiotic,

270
00:14:56,290 --> 00:14:56,810
so she can

271
00:14:56,810 --> 00:14:58,620
monitor every move of yours.

272
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:00,530
Zhuqing,

273
00:15:00,848 --> 00:15:02,410
she knows you take advantage of her

274
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:03,170
just now.

275
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:08,620
San,

276
00:15:09,170 --> 00:15:10,770
your taste is terrible.

277
00:15:11,260 --> 00:15:12,570
Wu won't tolerate it.

278
00:15:12,980 --> 00:15:13,770
Really?

279
00:15:15,290 --> 00:15:16,100
Look.

280
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:18,050
I think Wu looks pretty in anything.

281
00:15:23,290 --> 00:15:24,100
Wu,

282
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:25,020
let's go

283
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:26,260
and change clothes.

284
00:15:28,290 --> 00:15:29,020
I'll help you.

285
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:29,650
All right.

286
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:30,460
All of you

287
00:15:30,592 --> 00:15:31,376
go over there.

288
00:15:31,410 --> 00:15:31,890
Come on.

289
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:33,260
Wait over there.

290
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:34,140
No peeking.

291
00:15:35,690 --> 00:15:36,020
Come,

292
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:36,460
Wu.

293
00:15:37,290 --> 00:15:37,690
Let's go.

294
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:38,890
Stop watching her.

295
00:15:41,810 --> 00:15:42,290
Ao,

296
00:15:43,220 --> 00:15:44,100
is my taste that bad?

297
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:54,620
See?

298
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:55,584
She's gorgeous, right?

299
00:16:55,690 --> 00:16:57,530
This is how girls should dress like.

300
00:16:58,410 --> 00:16:58,770
Go.

301
00:17:03,808 --> 00:17:05,130
(Girls always have better taste)

302
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,980
(when it comes to clothing.)

303
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:09,370
Wu says she likes it.

304
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:11,330
If Fatty finds out

305
00:17:11,810 --> 00:17:12,740
Wu is back,

306
00:17:13,050 --> 00:17:14,330
he'll be surprised for sure.

307
00:17:14,980 --> 00:17:16,460
The Shrek Seven Devils

308
00:17:16,770 --> 00:17:17,980
are finally reunited again.

309
00:17:28,260 --> 00:17:30,220
Fatty and Xiang have gone out
for a while.

310
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:31,700
Why haven't they returned yet?

311
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:33,900
Boss Dai,

312
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,260
this is a rare chance
for them to go out.

313
00:17:36,336 --> 00:17:37,610
We have to give them a chance

314
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:39,090
to spend more time together.

315
00:17:40,130 --> 00:17:41,260
You know quite a lot.

316
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:51,130
Open it.

317
00:17:58,660 --> 00:17:59,260
Oh, Ma.

318
00:17:59,260 --> 00:17:59,850
Ma.

319
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:01,980
Finally, you're at my mercy.

320
00:18:03,088 --> 00:18:03,940
Beat me if you can.

321
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:04,740
Come on.

322
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:05,610
Come.

323
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:12,570
Miss Bai,

324
00:18:13,330 --> 00:18:14,850
I find

325
00:18:14,850 --> 00:18:16,096
the way you fled familiar.

326
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:18,610
Were you the one

327
00:18:18,688 --> 00:18:20,048
who ruined my plan at the tavern

328
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,850
that day with Ma?

329
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:23,500
Speak up.

330
00:18:28,740 --> 00:18:29,700
Capture her.

331
00:18:44,020 --> 00:18:44,570
Ma.

332
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:47,530
You go first.

333
00:18:58,320 --> 00:19:00,330
I'm talking to you.
Why are you looking at him?

334
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:08,330
Don't tell me you have bad taste

335
00:19:08,992 --> 00:19:10,050
and actually like him.

336
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,610
I'm pretty good.

337
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,700
How about considering...

338
00:19:16,740 --> 00:19:17,220
Ouch!

339
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,220
Let go.

340
00:19:19,770 --> 00:19:20,770
You wench!

341
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:22,530
Wench!

342
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:25,700
Boss!

343
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:26,460
Boss!

344
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:30,260
Hold him down!

345
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:33,330
Ma!

346
00:19:33,330 --> 00:19:34,700
How dare you!

347
00:19:34,770 --> 00:19:35,420
Ma Hongjun.

348
00:19:36,460 --> 00:19:37,220
Stop it!

349
00:19:37,770 --> 00:19:38,220
Enough.

350
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:39,120
Don't be impulsive.

351
00:19:39,130 --> 00:19:40,340
Chief said not to kill him yet.

352
00:19:40,352 --> 00:19:41,040
Please calm down.

353
00:19:41,104 --> 00:19:41,770
Calm down.

354
00:19:41,770 --> 00:19:42,740
Mark my words.

355
00:19:43,130 --> 00:19:44,850
Once the chief
takes over the four tribes,

356
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,020
you'll be in great trouble.

357
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:46,810
That's right.

358
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:53,940
Are you all right?

359
00:19:57,900 --> 00:19:59,130
I remember now.

360
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,420
Someone helped me that day.

361
00:20:02,090 --> 00:20:03,460
But they had their face covered,

362
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:05,330
so I couldn't see them clearly.

363
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:08,220
So it was you.

364
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,610
Why isn't Tang San here yet?

365
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:18,810
I'm waiting for his
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng.

366
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:21,810
Old Goat, calm down.

367
00:20:22,220 --> 00:20:23,020
When San is here,

368
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:25,220
the treasure will be yours.

369
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:27,980
Look.

370
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:28,660
He's here.

371
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:29,740
Hurry up.

372
00:20:33,090 --> 00:20:33,810
Isn't this girl

373
00:20:33,810 --> 00:20:35,330
the one who fought with me?

374
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:37,660
She's Wu.

375
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,220
She's my beloved.

376
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:42,420
Seniors,

377
00:20:42,672 --> 00:20:44,288
she doesn't have consciousness now,

378
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:45,780
so she's unable to greet you properly.

379
00:20:45,980 --> 00:20:47,130
Please forgive her.

380
00:20:49,984 --> 00:20:51,392
She lost her consciousness?

381
00:20:52,130 --> 00:20:53,570
Is it a brain trauma,

382
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:54,900
fright,

383
00:20:55,570 --> 00:20:56,370
or poisoning?

384
00:20:56,928 --> 00:20:57,700
None of those.

385
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,180
None of those?

386
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:01,700
Her complexion is rosy,

387
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:02,940
and she has a round forehead.

388
00:21:03,810 --> 00:21:06,530
This is a sign of great vitality.

389
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:08,610
She almost killed me.

390
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:11,330
This is a rare condition.

391
00:21:11,330 --> 00:21:13,900
She's healthy but without consciousness.

392
00:21:14,330 --> 00:21:16,220
If you trust my Yangs' healing skills,

393
00:21:16,530 --> 00:21:18,460
I'll try to diagnose her

394
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:19,810
and find the cause.

395
00:21:20,850 --> 00:21:22,460
Of course, I trust your skills,

396
00:21:23,088 --> 00:21:26,640
but Wu is a hectomillennium soul beast
before transforming into a human form.

397
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:28,660
She sacrificed herself

398
00:21:29,216 --> 00:21:30,736
to rescue me from Martial Soul Hall

399
00:21:31,130 --> 00:21:32,180
and almost perished.

400
00:21:32,740 --> 00:21:34,530
Even though her body has been restored,

401
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:35,740
she lost consciousness.

402
00:21:36,370 --> 00:21:37,500
With her current state,

403
00:21:37,940 --> 00:21:39,770
healing skills can't help her much.

404
00:21:40,370 --> 00:21:41,660
I see.

405
00:21:43,370 --> 00:21:44,370
Surprisingly,

406
00:21:44,810 --> 00:21:46,460
you and your father

407
00:21:46,940 --> 00:21:48,530
have such similar fates.

408
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:56,900
Anyway, don't lose hope.

409
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:59,370
If Old Goat

410
00:21:59,770 --> 00:22:01,530
joins the Tang Clan,

411
00:22:02,180 --> 00:22:04,050
he'll slowly treat

412
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:05,370
Miss Wu.

413
00:22:05,370 --> 00:22:07,420
Perhaps there's still hope.

414
00:22:07,980 --> 00:22:08,420
Right,

415
00:22:08,420 --> 00:22:09,260
Old Goat?

416
00:22:09,260 --> 00:22:09,660
Yes.

417
00:22:10,020 --> 00:22:11,460
If you can join us,

418
00:22:11,660 --> 00:22:12,610
I'll be very glad.

419
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:15,810
I heard

420
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:18,850
you have a precious gift

421
00:22:18,850 --> 00:22:19,980
for me.

422
00:22:21,330 --> 00:22:22,130
I'm ashamed to say

423
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:23,130
I was rude today,

424
00:22:23,168 --> 00:22:24,976
but you've treated me
with kindness instead.

425
00:22:25,024 --> 00:22:26,500
I was too assertive before.

426
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,940
I hope you won't mind.

427
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:30,900
I wouldn't dare.

428
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:32,020
You flatter me.

429
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:35,370
The gift for you is
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng.

430
00:22:38,570 --> 00:22:39,500
However,

431
00:22:39,728 --> 00:22:41,568
I'm afraid I can't present it to you.

432
00:22:42,176 --> 00:22:43,980
Because the Crystal Bloody
Dragon Ginseng

433
00:22:45,370 --> 00:22:46,370
was eaten by Wu.

434
00:22:47,850 --> 00:22:49,370
What did you just say?

435
00:22:49,370 --> 00:22:51,050
You ate such an immortal herb?

436
00:22:51,050 --> 00:22:51,850
Right.

437
00:22:53,936 --> 00:22:54,530
Old White Bird.

438
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:55,770
Don't worry, sir.

439
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:57,570
I've prepared another immortal herb.

440
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:58,610
No need.

441
00:22:58,736 --> 00:22:59,810
There's no immortal herb

442
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:03,090
rarer than Crystal Bloody
Dragon Ginseng.

443
00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,740
Forget it.

444
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:07,500
Seems like I'm not fated to have it.

445
00:23:07,810 --> 00:23:08,260
Sir,

446
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:11,130
I know Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng
is rare.

447
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:12,610
But

448
00:23:14,784 --> 00:23:15,810
please look at this.

449
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:20,980
Young Master,

450
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:24,050
Old Goat agreed to join Tang Clan

451
00:23:24,050 --> 00:23:25,610
for Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng.

452
00:23:26,020 --> 00:23:27,130
But it's gone now,

453
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:29,850
nothing will work,
no matter what you show him.

454
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,260
Old Goat,

455
00:23:34,420 --> 00:23:36,980
he didn't mean that.

456
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,130
This is

457
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:50,020
the Fragrant Silk Woven Flower?

458
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:51,330
Precisely.

459
00:23:52,290 --> 00:23:52,980
Are you sure

460
00:23:53,980 --> 00:23:55,180
you want to give me this?

461
00:23:55,610 --> 00:23:56,260
That's right.

462
00:23:56,608 --> 00:23:57,700
It chooses its own master.

463
00:23:58,180 --> 00:23:59,740
I believe it will be more useful

464
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:01,370
in your hand.

465
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:03,850
I have some knowledge of herbs,

466
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:06,330
and I hope I can seek your guidance.

467
00:24:14,420 --> 00:24:14,850
Very well.

468
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:15,980
Very well.

469
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:18,180
I'll follow you from now on.

470
00:24:20,090 --> 00:24:21,770
You must keep your word.

471
00:24:21,770 --> 00:24:23,020
I will.

472
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,660
(I was feeling guilty)

473
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:32,976
(about accidentally consuming)

474
00:24:32,992 --> 00:24:34,400
(the Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng,)

475
00:24:34,432 --> 00:24:36,432
(but it seems
you have planned out everything.)

476
00:24:36,610 --> 00:24:37,130
(Of course.)

477
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:38,900
(I'm always prepared.)

478
00:24:39,024 --> 00:24:41,360
(Thanks to Granduncle's
Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng,)

479
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:42,610
(if not,)

480
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,416
(I didn't know how long
I'd have to wait)

481
00:24:44,530 --> 00:24:46,050
(to speak with you like this.)

482
00:24:48,740 --> 00:24:50,740
I've been searching for it for life.

483
00:24:51,660 --> 00:24:54,090
Fragrant Silk Woven Flower...

484
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:56,020
With you,

485
00:24:56,420 --> 00:24:58,660
I'll have no fear
in concocting any poison.

486
00:25:00,050 --> 00:25:00,660
Old Goat,

487
00:25:00,810 --> 00:25:02,050
didn't you say

488
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,664
that my Crystal Bloody Dragon Ginseng

489
00:25:03,810 --> 00:25:04,770
was the most valuable?

490
00:25:05,050 --> 00:25:08,180
Fragrant Silk Woven Flower
can combat all the poisons.

491
00:25:08,180 --> 00:25:10,050
It can't detoxify,
but it can resist poison.

492
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,700
With it, I don't have to fear poisoning
while refining medicine.

493
00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:15,900
To the Tribe of Destruction,

494
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:17,900
this is priceless.

495
00:25:18,530 --> 00:25:20,700
I'm willing to trade it
with my own life.

496
00:25:20,928 --> 00:25:22,240
He's so obsessed with it.

497
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:23,900
Oh no!

498
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,330
Old Goat has lost his mind

499
00:25:27,136 --> 00:25:28,220
because of this flower.

500
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:30,130
Tang San,

501
00:25:30,336 --> 00:25:31,460
you're really something.

502
00:25:32,112 --> 00:25:33,460
You shouldn't call him by his name.

503
00:25:33,850 --> 00:25:35,660
We're members of the Tang Clan now,

504
00:25:35,660 --> 00:25:36,530
so we should call him

505
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:37,810
the chief.

506
00:25:38,050 --> 00:25:39,130
All of you are my seniors,

507
00:25:39,500 --> 00:25:41,130
and you'll be the clan elders.

508
00:25:41,420 --> 00:25:43,460
Friends older than me and my seniors

509
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,290
call me San.

510
00:25:44,660 --> 00:25:46,610
I hope you'll do the same.

511
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,220
Sure.

512
00:25:48,610 --> 00:25:49,940
San.

513
00:25:54,130 --> 00:25:54,850
Move.

514
00:25:55,104 --> 00:25:56,480
Something bad has happened!

515
00:25:57,850 --> 00:25:58,530
Kneel.

516
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,020
I was just about to take a walk

517
00:26:01,370 --> 00:26:03,610
when I saw this fellow sneaking around
at the gate.

518
00:26:03,792 --> 00:26:04,940
I came to deliver a letter.

519
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:05,810
I have a letter.

520
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:13,660
(To meet with you, I've invited Miss Bai Chenxiang.
I'll await your arrival. From Huyan Zhen)

521
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:21,050
What did you do to Xiang?

522
00:26:21,570 --> 00:26:23,610
The chief would like
to invite the four of you

523
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:24,810
to Elephant Armored Tribe.

524
00:26:24,980 --> 00:26:28,220
Miss Bai Chenxiang
has been waiting there.

525
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,850
Huyan Zhen must've set up traps.

526
00:26:30,370 --> 00:26:31,330
We need to be prepared.

527
00:26:34,370 --> 00:26:36,260
This darned Huyan Zhen!

528
00:26:36,770 --> 00:26:40,460
I'm going to destroy
the Elephant Armored Tribe.

529
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:43,020
This letter specifically calls for

530
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,810
the four single attribute tribes.

531
00:26:45,330 --> 00:26:48,020
Looks like we're meeting
Huyan Zhen together.

532
00:26:49,181 --> 00:26:50,451
He's dead meat!

533
00:26:51,552 --> 00:26:54,624
(Longxing Town)

534
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:20,100
(Elephant Armored)

535
00:27:20,370 --> 00:27:20,980
Huyan Zhen,

536
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:22,130
you vile scoundrel!

537
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:23,420
Come out!

538
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:26,900
(Elephant Armored)

539
00:27:26,900 --> 00:27:29,810
Everyone says the four tribes are tight,

540
00:27:31,260 --> 00:27:33,020
and now I see it.

541
00:27:33,290 --> 00:27:35,090
You lackey of the Martial Soul Hall,

542
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:37,020
where's my granddaughter?

543
00:27:37,530 --> 00:27:38,570
If you dare to hurt her,

544
00:27:39,090 --> 00:27:40,660
I'll take you down to hell

545
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:42,570
even at the cost of my life.

546
00:27:42,770 --> 00:27:43,500
Mr. Bai,

547
00:27:44,090 --> 00:27:45,420
simmer down.

548
00:27:46,020 --> 00:27:47,420
Miss Bai is my guest.

549
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:48,770
How could I harm her?

550
00:27:49,420 --> 00:27:51,900
I believe you know what I mean.

551
00:27:53,220 --> 00:27:56,460
Please submit to
the Elephant Armored Tribe.

552
00:27:56,928 --> 00:27:58,500
There's no need to make things ugly

553
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:00,290
over a trivial matter.

554
00:28:00,570 --> 00:28:01,370
As if!

555
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:04,180
You actually abducted Xiang

556
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,664
to coerce us to submit to you.

557
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,720
I, Yang Wudi, will never

558
00:28:06,770 --> 00:28:08,810
join you despicable scum.

559
00:28:09,130 --> 00:28:10,500
It's fine if you don't agree,

560
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:13,500
but if Miss Bai gets injured

561
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:16,500
or is poisoned

562
00:28:17,290 --> 00:28:18,940
in our tribe,

563
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:20,020
I can't make any promises.

564
00:28:20,020 --> 00:28:21,090
You!

565
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:25,290
Sirs,

566
00:28:25,850 --> 00:28:27,180
you have 15 minutes.

567
00:28:28,090 --> 00:28:29,180
Sirs,

568
00:28:29,530 --> 00:28:30,770
take your time.

569
00:29:00,180 --> 00:29:01,330
Stop trying.

570
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:03,020
You've been poisoned.

571
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,020
If you force your soul power,

572
00:29:05,020 --> 00:29:07,392
the poison will only enter
